BA Cancels Flights Between London, Scotland Until 2P.M. Tomorrow

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-23T20:35:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-23/ba-cancels-flights-between-london-scotland-until-2p-m-tomorrow.html
British Airways Plc has canceled all
flights between  London  and Scotland tomorrow until 2 p.m. local
time following forecasts of “significant” volcanic ash in
Scottish airspace, the company said in a  statement  on its
website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 